<br>
Leader-(n.) One who leads.<br>
<br>
<br>
My friends and Packmates,<br>
The past weeks have been a difficult time for the Pack. I think everyone has sensed a degree of tension amongst us. We have been walking in limbo, without a sense of direction or purpose. Not moving forward or backward...just standing still. Morale is low and we can not afford to continue this course of action. Many of you have brought your recent concerns about the state of the Pack to myself and the other Elders. I want you all to know that those concerns have not fallen upon deaf ears. It was decided by the Elder Counsil that a change needed to be made. This change was intended to happen at the Officer's meeting that we are trying to organize. Due to the urgency of some issues, and the insistence of certain individuals involved, it was decided to do it sooner. <br>
<br>
That being said, it is my duty to inform you that as of yesterday evening I have accepted the fate that was decided for me months before. It is time for me to do what Leetah wanted me to do when she resigned. It is time for me to wear the mantle of Leadership and guide the Aegis Wolves to a new age of glory. At Adlehardt's request, he has resigned his commision as a Pack Elder as well. I want you all to understand that I bear no ill will towards Adle for his decision, and I would like the rest of you to do the same. He has been a friend to me ever since the day we met and will always have my respect. <br>
<br>
I wish to thank all of you that have come forward with your questions, comments, concerns and ideas. All I can say is please, keep them coming. If you do not speak your mind nothing will ever get done. Communication is vital to our success. As the saying goes, my door is always open. Unless I am dead, dying, running from a train or saving someone's life, I am always willing to find a patch of grass, sit down with a beer and chat with someone for as long as they would like to talk, about whatever is on their mind. My contact information is posted in Scent Markers, as is the contact information for Forin and Jonan. Please use it. If there is something on your mind, let us know. Until then...good journeys to you all.<br>
<br>
Kronenburg Ponykeg<br>
Paladin of Underfoot<br>
Husband to Yonder Wendobrayxe<br>
